annotationA: WW domain-containing oxidoreductase; Putative oxidoreductase. May control genotoxic stress- induced cell death. May play a role in TGFB1 signaling and TGFB1- mediated cell death. May also play a role in tumor necrosis factor (TNF)-mediated cell death. May play a role in Wnt signaling (By similarity)
annotationB: Transcription factor AP-2, isoform D; Transcription factor AP-2 (TfAP-2) is a transcription factor with essential roles in leg, proboscis, and central nervous system development. TfAP-2 mediates Notch signaling in the developing tarsus
